{"h79188685g546ag4663ga298g8ff2259af4d5": ["*The parasite seizes as you approach.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "5ce90ce3-238b-28e6-5621-d1cff2f9698a"], "hd092111eg376eg40b2g863dg1bacccf6068a": ["You dare show your face?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "d43bc281-14af-430c-c38b-26936018b61e"], "hc268e327gaf41g4440g8c1agb3bc0be3d07a": ["Give me one reason why they shouldn't slay you where you stand.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "bfd3103f-48e6-118d-a0ae-acede330f106"], "h3c18b33fg93b0g4cb5ga66cgc4cba8cbf6d9": ["You need all the help you can get. Now stand down before I put you down.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "e3c78d2f-0e70-1a77-7b7f-04d70fc8b5ae"], "hde990a6fg4c3eg477eg9753gac1c3165c907": ["Fine - one last chance. See that you don't waste it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "215b8432-5367-9c06-5339-9d09780a4bd0"], "he9b44b16gfbdeg4409g843fg3b13f547622f": ["Inside, and hurry. I want that gate closed when the goblins get here.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "b61af41b-def8-0574-f055-7e50e279c29e"], "h8423876egc0e2g4ce9ga350g7a9d5b216365": ["You had your chance, and you wasted it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "e9fd829c-0cb9-2338-d32a-f86094022f3b"], "h3afe31f1g867fg4738gb1bcg0614d87101e0": ["In the name of the Blade, attack!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "c31c6a92-7d53-fbee-4b54-ff5bfca57e07"], "hd42d0fe8g516bg4c44gae5bga6cfce2cae31": ["The goblins are on their way. I've led them right into your trap.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "9479f1a8-fc24-4c04-9121-e9bb8dbb8cf0"], "h04b78a89g5540g427cgb593g5ccfc973d188": ["Did you, now?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "3b782bc9-3773-1524-2825-a87966fabe6c"], "h3ef6a399gdbadg468bg8da3gad110d8b560e": ["I hate to admit it, but... it's a good plan. Looks like the team's back together.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "356afc90-97a0-7ca6-3cd5-a14a0c2c2aa1"], "hf1a1c293gdd4eg4481g97d1ga90f9d96cb49": ["Let them try.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "5b087c63-0a3f-3c37-8dac-21e41c0315e7"], "hd6354562g283fg4e47ga9f7gc932068fc534": ["*The parasite seizes as you approach.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeetingWyll.html", "6e867cfd-3e93-c579-010b-bcce94274293"]}